Direct Known Subclasses:
DelegatingArray, DelegatingBlob, DelegatingClob, DelegatingDriver, DelegatingPooledConnection, DelegatingSQLInput, DelegatingSQLXML, DelegatingWrapper
public class DelegatingObject<T>
extends Object

This immutable class provides the ability to wrap an instance of T for delegation. This class only delegates toString(), subclasses may override Object.equals(Object) and Object.hashCode() to conform to their respective contracts.
